Class Bind

Annotation used by BoundFieldModule to indicate that a field should be bound to its value using Guice.

{@Bind} supports binding annotations. For example, to bind a {@code @Fast Car}, use {@code @Bind @Fast Car}.

Binding to {@code null} is only allowed for fields that are annotated {@code @Nullable}. See https://github.com/google/guice/wiki/UseNullable @see BoundFieldModule @author eatnumber1@google.com (Russ Harmon)
